step.reason:
\text{Matrix multiplication is}\textbf{ associative }\text{whenever}\\
A\times B \text{ and $B \times C$ are defined.Therefore,}\\
(AB)_{p \times r}\,C_{r \times s} = A_{p \times q}\,(BC)_{q \times s}= (ABC)_{p \times s}

step.context:
\text{What is the product of the following matrix}\\
\text{multiplication}\\
\left[\begin{array}{ccc}
x & -5 & -1 \end{array} \right]_{1 \times 3}
\left[\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & 2 \\ 
0 & 2 & 1 \\
2 & 0 & 3 \end{array} \right]_{3 \times 3}
\text{?}

step.reason:
A_{m \times n} \times B_{n \times p} = C_{m \times p} = [c_{ik}]_{m \times p}\\
 \text{where, } c_{ik}  = 
\displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n}a_{ij}\;b_{jk}

